OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778580402
OL,3,CStarmer: If we don't get this right,
OL,4,Cour country will go down a very dark
OL,5,Cpath
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer vowed to prove his
OL,8,F"doubters" wrong as he delivered a
OL,9,Fmajor speech aimed at averting a
OL,10,Fpotential leadership challenge.
OL,12,FThe prime minister promised sweeping
OL,13,Fchanges to address the "big
OL,14,Fchallenges" facing the UK, as he
OL,15,Ffought to save his job following a
OL,16,Fbruising set of local election results
OL,17,Fand subsequent calls for his
OL,18,Fresignation.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778580402
OL,3,CStarmer: If we don't get this right,
OL,4,Cour country will go down a very dark
OL,5,Cpath
OL,7,FDescribing Friday's results as tough,
OL,8,FSir Keir Starmer claimed the country
OL,9,Fwas facing both "dangerous times" and
OL,10,F"dangerous opponents".
OL,12,F"If we don't get this right, our
OL,13,Fcountry will go down a very dark
OL,14,Fpath," claimed the PM.
OL,16,F"I know people are frustrated by the
OL,17,Fstate of Britain, frustrated by
OL,18,Fpolitics, and some people, frustrated
OL,19,Fwith me," said Starmer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778580402
OL,3,CStarmer: If we don't get this right,
OL,4,Cour country will go down a very dark
OL,5,Cpath
OL,7,F"I know I have my doubters, I know I
OL,8,Fneed to prove them wrong, and I will."
OL,10,F'I know I have my doubters, and I know
OL,11,FI need to prove them wrong, and I
OL,12,Fwill,' says Starmer
OL,14,FThe prime minister went on to promise
OL,15,Fchange on defence, Europe, and energy,
OL,16,Fsaying "we need a bigger response than
OL,17,Fwe anticipated in 2024, because these
OL,18,Fare not ordinary times."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778580402
OL,3,CStarmer: If we don't get this right,
OL,4,Cour country will go down a very dark
OL,5,Cpath
OL,7,FSetting out his own position, Starmer
OL,8,Fsaid: "Strength through fairness, that
OL,9,Fis my compass in this world.
OL,11,F"In the coming days, you will see
OL,12,Fthose values writ large in The King's
OL,13,FSpeech, you will see hope, urgency,
OL,14,Fand exactly whose side we're on
OL,15,Freflected in everything we say and
OL,16,Feverything we do."
OL,18,FThe prime minister used his speech to
OL,19,Fpoint to three examples he said showed
OL,20,Fhis government's priorities and the
OL,21,Fdirection of travel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778580402
OL,3,CStarmer: If we don't get this right,
OL,4,Cour country will go down a very dark
OL,5,Cpath
OL,7,FDescribing it as "one of the proudest
OL,8,Fthings" he had done, Starmer
OL,9,Fhighlighted the support Labour gave to
OL,10,FBritish Steel in Scunthorpe last year,
OL,11,Fand promised further legislation this
OL,12,Fweek to take full national ownership
OL,13,Fof the company.
OL,15,FStarmer then went on to argue the case
OL,16,Ffor closer ties with Europe, labelling
OL,17,FNigel Farage as "not just a grifter",
OL,18,Fbut a "chancer".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778580402
OL,3,CStarmer: If we don't get this right,
OL,4,Cour country will go down a very dark
OL,5,Cpath
OL,7,FThe PM said the last government was
OL,8,Fdefined "by breaking our relationship
OL,9,Fwith Europe".
OL,11,F"This Labour government will be
OL,12,Fdefined by rebuilding our relationship
OL,13,Fwith Europe, by putting Britain at the
OL,14,Fheart of Europe," he said.
OL,16,FFinally, Starmer promised to "go
OL,17,Ffurther" on investment in
OL,18,Fapprenticeships, technical colleges,
OL,19,Fand special educational needs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778580402
OL,3,CStarmer: If we don't get this right,
OL,4,Cour country will go down a very dark
OL,5,Cpath
OL,7,F"This is nothing less than the battle
OL,8,Ffor the soul of our nation," Starmer
OL,9,Fconcluded in a final plea to both the
OL,10,Fpublic and his own party.
OL,12,F"I want to be crystal clear about how
OL,13,Fwe will win it.
OL,15,F"We can only win as a stronger version
OL,16,Fof Labour, a mainstream party of power.
OL,18,F"I will never stop fighting for the
OL,19,Fdecent, respectful, diverse country
OL,20,Fthat I love.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778580402
OL,3,CStarmer: If we don't get this right,
OL,4,Cour country will go down a very dark
OL,5,Cpath
OL,7,F"I will never give up on the hope we
OL,8,Fcan unlock in this country.
OL,10,F"A country taking control of its
OL,11,Ffuture, our spirit unchanged, our
OL,12,Fresolve unbroken, the hope of a
OL,13,Fcountry that can and will become a
OL,14,Fstronger, fairer Britain."
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
