OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778580402
OL,3,CStarmer: If we don't get this right,
OL,4,Cour country will go down a very dark
OL,5,Cpath
OL,7,FFollowing the catastrophic election
OL,8,Fresults on Friday, Starmer has faced
OL,9,Fcalls to resign and threats of
OL,10,Fleadership challenges.
OL,12,FLabour backbencher Catherine West has
OL,13,Fsaid she could try to challenge
OL,14,FStarmer's leadership if the Cabinet
OL,15,Fdoes not force him out, but Starmer
OL,16,Fhas vowed to stay on and see through
OL,17,Fwhat he calls his "10-year project"
OL,18,Ffor the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778580402
OL,3,CStarmer: If we don't get this right,
OL,4,Cour country will go down a very dark
OL,5,Cpath
OL,7,FBut MPs on Labour's left have warned
OL,8,Fagainst her plan, arguing it could
OL,9,Fresult in a Cabinet "stitch-up" rather
OL,10,Fthan allowing members to vote on the
OL,11,Fnext leader.
OL,13,FWest has herself pledged to give the
OL,14,FPM a hearing; she has made clear,
OL,15,Fhowever, that her campaign is an
OL,16,Fattempt to force the Cabinet to get
OL,17,Fbehind a candidate to move against
OL,18,FStarmer, rather than a credible
OL,19,Fchallenge to win the keys to No 10
OL,20,Fherself.
OL,26,@qD@UOUqD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778580402
OL,3,CStarmer: If we don't get this right,
OL,4,Cour country will go down a very dark
OL,5,Cpath
OL,7,FAsked whether he had himself
OL,8,Fconsidered resigning, Starmer said he
OL,9,Fwould not put the country through
OL,10,F"what we witnessed under the last
OL,11,Fgovernment.
OL,13,F"The chaos of constantly changing
OL,14,Fleaders... it costs this country."
OL,16,FStarmer's speech comes ahead of the
OL,17,FKing's Speech on Wednesday, which will
OL,18,Fset out his government's priorities
OL,19,Fand agenda for the next parliamentary
OL,20,Fsession.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778580402
OL,3,CStarmer: If we don't get this right,
OL,4,Cour country will go down a very dark
OL,5,Cpath
OL,7,FOne potential leadership candidate,
OL,8,Fformer Deputy PM Angela Rayner, is
OL,9,Falso set to deliver a speech in a
OL,10,Fseparate location shortly after the
OL,11,FPM's.
OL,13,FRayner wrote this weekend that, "the
OL,14,Fprime minister must now meet the
OL,15,Fmoment and set out the change our
OL,16,Fcountry needs," adding that it was a
OL,17,Fmistake to block potential leadership
OL,18,Fhopeful Andy Burnham from returning to
OL,19,Fparliament.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
